<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Parolni Tiklash - UltraMarket</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #1f2937;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #b91c1c;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .link {
            word-break: break-all;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .warning {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">UltraMarket</div>
            <h1 class="title">Parolni Tiklash</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Assalomu alaykum <strong>{{firstName}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>Hisobingiz uchun parolni tiklash so'rovi yuborildi. Agar bu siz bo'lsangiz, quyidagi tugmani bosib yangi parol o'rnating:</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="btn">Parolni Tiklash</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>Agar tugma ishlamasa, quyidagi havolani brauzeringizga nusxalang:</p>
            <p class="link">{{resetLink}}</p>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <p><strong>⚠️ Muhim xavfsizlik ma'lumotlari:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Bu havola 1 soat davomida amal qiladi</li>
                    <li>Havola faqat bir marta ishlatilishi mumkin</li>
                    <li>Agar siz bu so'rovni yubormagan bo'lsangiz, darhol bizga xabar bering</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>Agar siz parolni tiklashni so'ramagan bo'lsangiz, bu xabarni e'tiborsiz qoldiring. Sizning hisobingiz xavfsiz.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Hurmat bilan,<br>UltraMarket xavfsizlik jamoasi</p>
            <p>Bu avtomatik xabar. Iltimos, javob bermang.</p>
            <p>Yordam kerak bo'lsa: security@ultramarket.uz</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>